* Requirements

ANCI C++ compliant compiler, standard compliant C++ STL

cmake

make

xerces-c library

freetype2 library
 
transfig/fig2dev

Recommended: xfig

* Building from source (distribution tarball)

This project uses the standard GNU configure build flow. See the file
INSTALL for generic install instructions.

* Building from source (Subversion snapshot)

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ../
make

* Debugging

Disable optimization:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE='Debug' 
make

